{"tid":2263003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【藍店收皮】I.T上半年虧損4.14億","createTime":"2020-10-29T14:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T15:22:40.000Z","uid":2054,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"76fc14888bf7547681f888cece83802ca1b0126c","tid":2263003,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"蘋果全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201029/KK57UM53TJAK5ERO27P5KUIGZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201029%2FKK57UM53TJAK5ERO27P5KUIGZA%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=bc0e39d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201029%2FKK57UM53TJAK5ERO27P5KUIGZA%2F&h=e209205b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201029/KK57UM53TJAK5ERO27P5KUIGZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前已發盈警的本地潮牌I.T（999）公佈截至今年8月底止上半財年業績， 總營業額減少31.9%至27.34億元，經營開支按年減少21.7%至18.12億元，惜無助收窄業績虧損。期內虧損由去年同期的7,195.8萬元大幅擴大至3.37億元，董事會不宣派中期股息。<br />\n<br />\n業績虧損主要由於港澳市場期內錄4.14億元的經營虧損，該地區零售收入按年減少50.9%至7.19億元，同店銷售按年下跌48.9%，港澳期內淨關閉17間店舖，總銷售面積減幅達14.3%，較零售收入跌幅少。"},{"pid":"4824332a6e4791c5820b7aca1f1e8d1dcf314007","tid":2263003,"uid":104425,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"藍屍連買藍店當抗爭都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd53e0ceb46a8c1955e93981f78c6c53667af09c","tid":2263003,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"蝕入肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋當跌咗一蚊咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a457bdd05302716d7ddd38802cd707e7b28c388a","tid":2263003,"uid":2054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4sGBir.p